Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一直在想小吉說他做過的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just keep thinking about what Kier said he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復生時我們都做過極端的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we all took extreme measures during the Rising,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是嗎  史蒂夫  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- didn't we, Steve? - Yeah, I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們是為了自衛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we were defending ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我們要防的卻是他這種人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It turns out we were defending ourselves from people like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他當時不知道自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He didn't know what he was doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在每天都注射藥物  不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He takes his medication every day, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確  他曾有些精神錯亂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, at one time he was unbalanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他現在正常了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But... he's back to normal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你怎么了  兒子  -沒事啊  爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's going on, son? - Nothing, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他這副樣子我沒法看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't look at him when he's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉倫·沃克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kieren Walker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你被捕了  -被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're under arrest. - Arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天有人闖進診所  放走了狂暴僵尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}GP's were broke into yesterday, rabids were let loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僵尸攻擊了接待員  她入院了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They attacked the receptionist, she's in hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天哪  -闖進診所的不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Jesus! - I didn't break into the GP's surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我解釋也沒用  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not me who needs convincing. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要帶他去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, hey, where are you taking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教區理事會要問他話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Parish council want to question him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不能就這樣把他拖過去啊  -蘇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You can't just drag him off like this. - Sue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是馬丁小姐吩咐的  我必須帶他過去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orders from Miss Martin. I've got to bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸  媽  -你就這么傻站著嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mum? Dad? - Are you just going to stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說去就得去啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What she says goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽我說完嗎  我是想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you just give me a second, please? I am trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}忘記用藥一次就會發生以下情形\N警惕狂暴征兆\N不由自主的顫抖\N流鼻血\N失憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事的  沒事沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're fine, you're fine, you're fine, you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"您正在收聽諾頓調頻  在諾頓村為您播報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"You're listening to Roar FM, coming to you from down the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"今日首個話題當然就是《苦斗》"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"First topic of the day is, of course, Hard Graft."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不不  -"現在我們..."\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Oh, no, no, no. - "Now we..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-出什么事了  馬丁女士  -沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's wrong, Ms Martin? - I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你倒杯茶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get you a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清官難斷家務事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Parents can be the living end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不常跟我父親說話  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't speak to my father very often, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次說話  那真是一言難盡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when I do, it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不喜歡跟我爸媽說話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't like talking to mine neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們總是說個沒完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're always jabbering on and on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子永遠插不上嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}can never get a word in edgeways
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到走運才難得能跟我兄弟說上幾句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm lucky if I get to speak to my brother once in a blue moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我有個兄弟  -是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I have a brother. - Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥還是弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Older or younger?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他同我很親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's very dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最需要親人的時候  他們從來不在  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're never around when you need them most, though, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他的共犯在哪  -到處都找遍了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where's his accomplice? - Looked all over for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影兒都沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬丁女士堅持要他倆一起受審\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ms Martin was very insistent that they were tried together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跑了我們能怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What can we do if he's scarpered?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就你來交代吧  -交代什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Let's hear it from you, then. - Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我沒什么要認的  -胡說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Nothing to confess. - Rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那個愛爾蘭佬闖進診所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and that Irish one broke into the GP's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放掉的狂暴僵尸襲擊了接待員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and let loose rabids that mauled the receptionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被人引入歧途讓我心痛不已  吉倫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It saddens me that you've been so led astray, Kieren.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,襲擊之后  有人見到你和你的共犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and your accomplice were seen coming out of the GP's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從診所出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}after the mauling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和西蒙幾天前一起在診所工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Me and Simon worked together at the GP's a couple of days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就再也沒去過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we haven't been back since.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡在治療中心的日子嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you enjoy your time at the treatment centre?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你不認罪的話  就得回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cos that's where you're headed if you don't confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不能送我回諾福克  -要打賭嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You can't send me back to Norfolk! - Want to bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"如果半死癥患者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"If a PDS sufferer is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"被懷疑違反了釋放條例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"suspected of breaching their terms of release,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"須依照條例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"they must be reported
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"上報至半死癥事務部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"to the Department of Partially Deceased Affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"不合作的病人隨后將被拘留\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"whereupon the non-compliant patient will be detained
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"以防危害自身或他人安全"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"for their own safety and the safety of others."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有違反釋放條例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't breached my terms of release.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"對自身或公眾安危構成威脅的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"PDS patients who pose a threat to themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"半死癥患者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"or members of their community
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"將被視為危險分子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"are considered dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"須通知有關部門"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"and the proper authorities should be notified."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的共犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and your accomplice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經被認定對公眾構成了威脅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have been deemed a threat to your community.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我對公眾不構成威脅  -你是社區嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm not a threat to the community. - Are you the community?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我是公...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I am the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白你要問什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在問你  你是公眾嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm asking you, are you the community?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是  -沒錯  你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. - That's right, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才是公眾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are the community
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我們認為你對其構成了威脅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we have deemed you a threat to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖認罪 我們就給你緩刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, admit your guilt and we'll hand you a suspended sentence.
