Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去巡界嗎{\fs14}[傳統儀式]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beating The Bounds?
