Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這些野獸在四處游蕩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With those wild beasts still out and about,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不帶才怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}abso-bloody-lutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}諾頓教區理事會\N筆供
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我干的  爸爸  他們誣告我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't do it, Dad. I've been falsely accused.
