Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們威脅說要把他送回諾福克呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they're threatening to send him back to Norfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就該簽字認罪完事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right, so you should sign the confession and have done with it.
