Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒做的事我不會認罪的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not confessing to something I didn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是形勢所迫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were pressured into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了跟上潮流誰沒干過點蠢事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We all do daft things to join the in crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那年齡也叛逆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bloody hell, I've done my fair share of rebelling -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處敲門  敲完就跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}knock-a-door-runs all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西蒙鼓動你做的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did Simon put you up to it, love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  媽媽  他沒鼓動我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Mum, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  你們是我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God! You're supposed to be my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本該無條件支持我的  我知道他們會那樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have my back, no matter what. I expect it from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但回來還要被自己家人審嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but to be put on trial by my own family?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們暫停一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's call a clock out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去忙村民游園會的裝飾了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got to get on those decorations for the fete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上班要遲到了  我還以為你能待在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm late for work. I was hoping you could stop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么可能  史蒂夫  -好吧  好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How can I, Steve? - All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平靜下來了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you calmed down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會亂來吧  我們把你一人留在家里的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll behave, won't you, if we leave you here on your tod?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"您正在收聽諾頓調頻"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"You're listening to Roar FM."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我們連線了特雷弗  你好特雷弗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"We've got Trevor on the line. Hi, Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-"你好  戴夫"  -"你對半死癥怎么看"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- "How do, Dave?" - "What's your PDS point of view?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我很擔憂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Well, I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"今日一篇報道半死癥患者產生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"There's a piece in paper today about these PDS sufferers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"耐藥性的文章見諸報端"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"becoming tolerant to their medications."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-"令人震驚  特雷弗"  -"很恐怖"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- "Scary stuff, Trev." - "Terrifying."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我聽到這消息一點不吃驚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"I wouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"科學家跟政府一樣鬼話連篇不可信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"I trust the scientists as much as I trust the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.57,0:22:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我媽媽治偏頭疼的藥就不管用了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Me mother's migraine pills stopped working."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what are you up to, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是隨手修修東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just doing a spot of DIY.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾森家還真是驚喜連連啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wow. The excitement never stops in the Wilson household!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去一日游\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Going on a day trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想你要不要陪我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was wondering if you wanted to accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是禁止旅游嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about the travel ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我們要去哪兒  延巴克圖嗎{\fs14}[西非城市]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where do you think we're going, Timbuktu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們去哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去個瘋狂的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somewhere crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你打過瘋狂{\fs14}[迷你]{\fs}高爾夫嗎  -沒有  這是頭一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Have you never played crazy golf before? - No, first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你直是推球天才\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a putting natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-也許我今天走運  -慢著  泰格{\fs14}[著名高爾夫球手]{\fs}\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Maybe I'm just lucky today. - Whoa, there, Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋狂高爾夫可是技巧性運動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Crazy golf is a game of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然怎么會是奧運會比賽項目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wouldn't be an Olympic sport if it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是奧運會項目吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not sure it is an Olympic sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-為什么不是  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why not? - Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是因為名字叫"瘋狂高爾夫"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe because it's called "Crazy golf."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乒乓球的名字也很奇怪啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Table tennis is called Ping-Pong,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是奧運會項目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that's an Olympic sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒準把打瘋狂高爾夫的人聚在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps if the crazy golf people got together
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想個嚴肅點的名字  比如...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and came up with a more serious-sounding name, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復雜障礙高爾夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}elaborate obstacle golf,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時你再看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you see then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許奧組委就會把它算作體育項目了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then the olympic body might make it a proper sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是體育項目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is a proper sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.37,0:24:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管奧林匹斯山的諸神怎么說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't care what the gods of Olympus say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群破神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stupid gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  我感覺不到  不覺得冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's OK. I don't feel anything. Don't feel the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.64,0:24:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感覺到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you feel that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.27,0:24:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全沒知覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't feel a bloody thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.80,0:24:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也經常忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I forget meself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.04,0:25:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么急干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.07,0:25:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -你打得太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - You're really good at this,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.29,0:25:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再打一桿就贏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and if you take that shot then you're going to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.73,0:25:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戲就結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.25,0:25:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽不就是為了贏嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't that the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.88,0:25:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了能一直玩兒下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The point of a game is to keep on playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  也許吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.91,0:25:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果不比完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if we don't finish it,
