Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.27,0:25:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你再一桿進洞  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You get another hole-in-one,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.54,0:25:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸了的人就親你一口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you get a kiss from the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.43,0:25:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.09,0:26:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神  菲利普  集中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Focus, Phil, focus.
