Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.62,0:43:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以先試著別偏袒暴徒  爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can start by not siding with the mob, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.87,0:43:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是擔憂家人的安危罷了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm just concerned for this family's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.82,0:43:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.21,0:43:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.14,0:43:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你現在這個表現  我不如干脆承認\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll admit it. When you're acting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.60,0:43:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acting like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.76,0:43:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都快認不出你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't even recognise you any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.93,0:43:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.00,0:43:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.80,0:44:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}吉倫·沃克  親親
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.45,0:44:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-艾米  -進來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Amy? - In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.18,0:44:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到你的留言了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.53,0:44:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你能來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.93,0:44:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你的帳篷頂上扯破了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know you've got a tear at the top of your tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.99,0:45:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我要做的大事比  這微不足道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Small potatoes in the grand scheme of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.97,0:45:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是該帶個睡袋來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was I supposed to bring a sleeping bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.65,0:45:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復生的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}During the Rising...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.33,0:45:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺過狂暴僵尸嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}did you ever kill a rabid?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.96,0:45:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復生時  我是搞后勤的那種\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}During the Rising, I was more a back office sort of bloke.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.84,0:45:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺過也沒關系的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's ok if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.60,0:45:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能殺過更好點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Actually, it's better if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.72,0:45:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  我誰都沒殺過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I never killed anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.85,0:45:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有幫人安樂死過嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not even a sort of... mercy killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.26,0:45:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.80,0:45:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我戴上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put them on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.58,0:46:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著螺絲刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pick up the screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.68,0:46:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先告訴我你要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not until you tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.95,0:46:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um... I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.90,0:46:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經在5號登機樓了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm currently at Terminal 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.78,0:46:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李箱都收拾好了  我在候機室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got my suitcase packed, I'm in the departure lounge,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.34,0:46:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差上飛機了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just need to get on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.81,0:46:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.31,0:46:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.24,0:46:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對藥物產生了免疫性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've become immune to the medication,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.06,0:46:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我都沒有藥效了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the drugs aren't working any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.23,0:46:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快我就會恢復狂暴狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And not long from now, I'm going to go rabid,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.26,0:46:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且沒有藥物可以再讓我變回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and there's no chemicals out there that can turn me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.78,0:46:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想變回狂暴僵尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want to live as a rabid,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.43,0:46:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行尸走肉  到處害人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}going around hurting people without a thought in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.08,0:46:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種日子太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's no kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.49,0:46:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去給羅素醫生打電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll call Dr.Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.59,0:46:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的  一旦我變了就變不回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's no good. Once I turn, I turn for good and then I'm stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.73,0:46:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠那樣活著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stuck like that for ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.76,0:46:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生不如死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a fate worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.73,0:47:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你得在我變之前殺了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why I need you to put me down before I go rabid.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.01,0:47:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊  求您給我一個啟示吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lord, please, give me a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.35,0:47:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.72,0:47:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了  馬丁女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry to disturb, Miss Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.36,0:47:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was just wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.99,0:47:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是否想下來一起看大結局呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you wanted to come downstairs for the finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.54,0:47:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-大結局  -我追的偵探片《苦斗》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Finale? - Me detective show - Hard Graft.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.50,0:47:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連鎖超市最好的卡瓦酒  專為今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shop'n'Save's best cava for the big night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.51,0:47:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克萊夫  你不用這么費心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Clive, you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.43,0:47:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是重要場合  不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a big occasion, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.30,0:47:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《苦斗》的最后一集了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Final episode of Hard Graft.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.10,0:47:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是昨晚播的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That were on last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.46,0:47:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  媽媽  但桑德拉昨晚沒看上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, Mum, but Sandra didn't get to watch it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.89,0:47:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我錄下來了  我們今晚看好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I recorded it and we're watching it tonight, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.31,0:47:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Too bloody right we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.75,0:47:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.89,0:48:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終于能知道兇手是誰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I get to find out who the killer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.14,0:48:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是也很激動  馬丁女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you excited, too, Miss Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.38,0:48:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都坐不住了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Edge of me seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.02,0:48:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.97,0:48:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在屋里躲了一天呢  對吧克萊夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've not been out of the house all day, have I, Clive?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.46,0:48:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把自己鎖在臥室里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She locked herself in bedroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.45,0:48:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小時前才出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}didn't come out till an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.09,0:48:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就怕聽到劇透呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just in case I heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.68,0:48:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都別想破壞今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've made sure that nothing can spoil it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.86,0:48:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒禮貌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.70,0:48:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑德拉  你沒給媽媽倒酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandra, you left out Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.34,0:48:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不喝酒  她不能喝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She don't drink. She can't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.42,0:48:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會跟上次一樣穿腸而過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll go through you like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.26,0:48:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝一杯沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.95,0:48:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-桑德拉  給她一杯吧  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sandra, give her a glass, eh? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.72,0:48:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小時后  還得我去收拾她的爛攤子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cos in an hour I'll be cleaning up her mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.24,0:48:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒戲  今晚不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No way. Not tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.71,0:48:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我最大  什么都不給她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tonight's my night. She gets nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.03,0:48:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探長約翰·格萊福特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Detective Inspector John Graft,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.16,0:48:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  魁梧粗獷的約克郡男子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thank you, you rugged Yorkshire hunk of stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.93,0:48:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我們所有人的生活都添了些許精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for bringing a little bit of excitement into all our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.79,0:48:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看節目吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now on with the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.61,0:48:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兇手是約翰·格萊福特的父親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}John Graft's dad is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.32,0:48:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚看了大結局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw the finale last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.62,0:48:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兇手一直是約翰·格萊福特的父親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turns out John Graft's dad were the killer all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.69,0:48:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前任警長就是他殺的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was the one who killed the ex-police captain
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.99,0:49:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為80年代的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}cos back in the '80s,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.43,0:49:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警長打遍了和他一起筑人墻的好哥們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the captain beat up all the dad's mates on the picket line.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.94,0:49:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老早就看出神轉折了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Saw that plot twist a mile off.
