Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.61,0:49:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個邪惡的老巫婆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You rotten, evil hag.
