Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.69,0:49:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要說  吉姆  吉姆  吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim! Jim! Jim! Jim! Jimmy!
